Package: xopt
Type: Package
Title: State-of-the-Art Optimization with Automatic Differentiation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2026-04-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("Angel", "Robles", email = "angel.robles@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Modern optimization framework combining quasi-Newton BFGS (ucminfcpp),
    automatic differentiation (XAD), and zero-copy tensor operations (xtensor-r).
    Provides efficient gradient-based optimization with C++20 compiled objectives
    for maximum performance on statistical and scientific computing problems.
License: AGPL-3
SystemRequirements: C++20
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0)
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
URL: https://github.com/alrobles/xopt
BugReports: https://github.com/alrobles/xopt/issues
